    <h1>5- PB Influencer scheme disbursal and compliance- Ops SOP</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 id=3D"id-5-PBInfluencerschemedisbursalandcompliance-OpsSOP-Purp=
oseandScope"><strong>Purpose and Scope</strong></h2>
<p>To smoothen scheme disbursal, influencer KYC and gifting process for Dis=
tributor-led schemes and ensure timely payouts to vendors.</p>
<p><strong>Handover timeline: PB -&gt;BizOps: </strong><time datetime=3D"20=
25-09-08" class=3D"date-past">08 Sep 2025</time></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-5-PBInfluencerschemedisbursalandcompliance-OpsSOP-Stakeholders=
"><strong>Stakeholders</strong></h2>
<p>Influencer data sharing - PB sales</p>
<p>Influencer verification - Inside Sales</p>
<p>Data collation and customer/sales followups - BizOps</p>
<p>Scheme calculations - PB team</p>
<p>PO issuance to vendors - Marketing/BizOps <em>(To be aligned)</em></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-5-PBInfluencerschemedisbursalandcompliance-OpsSOP-Steps"><stro=
ng>Steps</strong></h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Scheme data sourcing- Sales team to update influencer details in SF-&gt;=
Reports-&gt;Influencer sales data.</p></li>
<li>
<p>This data is to be verified by IS team through calls using a set of ques=
tionaires.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Post qualification of leads, PB team to compute list of qualified influe=
ncers basis tonnage and monthly business, and share the list with the respe=
ctive Distributors for confirmation.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Sheet link- <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://jsw-my.sharepoint=
.com/:x:/r/personal/supriya_sharan_jsw_in/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=3D=
%7BEFDB3FE6-AB98-4E56-AA13-E4EF8FED9D5F%7D&amp;file=3DInfluencer%20Scheme%2=
0-%20Qualifier%20List%20&amp;%20Gift%20Dispatch.xlsx=3D&amp;fromShare=3Dtru=
e&amp;action=3Ddefault&amp;mobileredirect=3Dtrue" rel=3D"nofollow">Influenc=
er Scheme - Qualifier List &amp; Gift Dispatch</a></p>
<ol start=3D"4">
<li>
<p>BizOps to then sync with the Distributor for alignment on the final list=
, and in case of any discrepancy, the Distributor needs to share edits and =
their own list on their letter head for BizOps' perusal, which shall be com=
municated via email.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Once the list is finalized, BizOps to connect to each influencer for the=
ir KYC document (currently- Aadhar), and needs to be uploaded via MS Form <=
em>(link to be provided by PB team)</em>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Matching/verification of final dispatch list wherein KYC status (success=
full, pending verification etc.) of finalised influencers needs to be updat=
ed.</p></li>
<li>
<p>PO to be then raised by Marketing/BizOps to our vendor on behalf of the =
Distributor, and needs to be shared with them as well.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Vendor payout to be followed up (by Marketing or BizOps whoever makes th=
e PO).</p></li>
<li>
<p>Gifts dispatch status to be finally tracked by PB/BizOps team.</p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p><strong>TAT for data updation:</strong></p>
<p>Quartely activity- To be completed within 3 weeks from previous quarter-=
end.</p>
<h2 id=3D"id-5-PBInfluencerschemedisbursalandcompliance-OpsSOP-ReviewandSig=
n-off"><strong>Review and Sign-off</strong></h2>
